1. Which of the following best defines CRM, Sales Cloud, and Salesforce?
Solution : B. Salesforce is the company that pioneered CRM in the cloud, and sales Cloud is a product it offers

2. Which sales best practice should you follow?
Solution : D. You should keep your customer information in one place, accessible by your whole team, so you can sell faster and smarter and be prepared to grow

3. Which of these is true about how Sales Cloud can help you grow your business?
Solution : C. Sales Cloud gives you real-time reports of how your business is doing
